text: Staff attitude problem I order char siu noodle the staff ask if I will add I'm ok it $2 add on .. when I see the portion.. it only total 7 pcs of char siu meat . I'm ok to pay the $2 but must give me a reasonable portion.  I won't recommend this stall n go again .. total $6.30 .
The Roost Duck is those Tang Gui flavor and the char siew is also half fat Lean meat type.. Roost pork skin is crispy too. Not bad!! But the dumpling meat like not well marinated. Not bad de..

Asked if there's QR payment option, stall lady told me no, my wife is next to me I asked her if she got smaller notes, the stall lady abruptly said she got change.. okie done, nothing to fuzz about. Sat down to have my food, another customer came on and ordered, they no cash, this time another stall fellow told them they can scan pay??!!! Simi standard. Apparently not owner, and I am referring to the roast delight lady cashier. Please sort her out
Roasted duck, chicken, pork belly, bbq chicken etc. Price and portion reasonable
